"""
================================================================================
                    SECURITY RECONNAISSANCE REPORT GENERATOR
                           Recon Dashboard v4.0
================================================================================

COMPREHENSIVE SECURITY REPORT GENERATION SYSTEM

This module generates professional, FAANG-level security reports in multiple
formats (PDF, HTML, Excel, Word, JSON, CSV, XML) with comprehensive vulnerability
details, proper text wrapping, readable fonts, and complete information display.

================================================================================
FEATURES
================================================================================

• Multi-format Export (PDF, HTML, Excel, Word, JSON, CSV, XML)
• No text truncation (full content with proper word wrapping)
• Large, readable fonts (9-14pt)
• Professional table layouts with proper column widths
• Complete vulnerability details (CVE, CVSS, References, Remediation)
• Risk scoring and prioritization (0-100 scale)
• Visual severity indicators with color coding
• DNS/SSL configuration analysis
• Nmap port scan results with risk assessment
• Technology stack detection and analysis
• Executive summary with KPIs and metrics
• Compliance checking (OWASP, PCI-DSS, HIPAA)
• Automated recommendations engine
• Chart and graph generation
• Appendix and glossary sections
• Comprehensive error handling and logging
• Template-based report generation
• Customizable branding and styling
• Batch report generation support
• Report versioning and archival
• Multi-language support (extensible)
• Accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1)

================================================================================
ARCHITECTURE
================================================================================

The report generator follows a modular, component-based architecture:

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    ReportGenerator (Main Class)                  │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  • ReportConfig (Configuration Management)                       │
│  • ReportStyles (Style Management)                               │
│  • TableBuilder (Table Construction)                             │
│  • VulnerabilityProcessor (Vulnerability Analysis)               │
│  • DNSSSLProcessor (DNS/SSL Analysis)                            │
│  • NmapProcessor (Port Scan Analysis)                            │
│  • TechnologyProcessor (Tech Stack Analysis)                     │
│  • RiskCalculator (Risk Scoring Engine)                          │
│  • RecommendationEngine (Recommendation Generator)               │
│  • ComplianceChecker (Compliance Validation)                     │
│  • ChartGenerator (Visual Chart Creation)                        │
│  • TemplateManager (Report Templates)                            │
│  • ExportManager (Multi-format Export)                           │
│  • ValidationUtils (Data Validation)                             │
│  • TextUtils (Text Processing)                                   │
│  • DateUtils (Date/Time Handling)                                │
│  • FileUtils (File Operations)                                   │
│  • LogUtils (Logging Utilities)                                  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

================================================================================
USAGE EXAMPLES
================================================================================

# Basic Usage
from services.report_generator import report_generator

# Generate report data
report_data = await report_generator.generate_report_data(db, scan_id)

# Export to different formats
pdf_bytes = report_generator.generate_pdf(report_data)
html_content = report_generator.generate_html(report_data)
excel_bytes = report_generator.generate_excel(report_data)
word_bytes = report_generator.generate_docx(report_data)
json_content = report_generator.generate_json(report_data)
csv_content = report_generator.generate_csv(report_data)
xml_content = report_generator.generate_xml(report_data)

# Advanced Usage with Options
options = {
    'include_appendix': True,
    'include_glossary': True,
    'include_charts': True,
    'include_recommendations': True,
    'include_compliance': True,
    'max_vulns_per_page': 15,
    'max_hosts_per_page': 20,
    'max_ports_per_page': 30,
    'color_scheme': 'professional',
    'paper_size': 'letter',
    'orientation': 'portrait'
}

pdf_bytes = report_generator.generate_pdf(report_data, options)

